  "intro": {
    "en-US": "Built for Spain trips where Renfe schedules, apartment check-ins, tapas stops, beach-town logistics, and late dinners all shape the day. These cards help when you need quick Spanish for train questions, menu del dia orders, or simple requests in smaller bars and neighborhood shops.",
    "zh-CN": "这套西班牙短语适合那种会遇到 Renfe 车次、民宿入住、tapas 小馆、海边城市出行和晚餐偏晚节奏的旅行路线。遇到要问火车、点 menu del dia，或者在小酒馆与社区店里提出简短需求时，短语卡会很有帮助。"
  },
  "teaser": {
